snippet.title: Kitty Cat Jigsaw Puzzles - Trailer
snippet.description: Kitty Cat Jigsaw Puzzles is loaded with 84 different jigsaw puzzles made from pictures of cute and lovely kittens.  A star rating system that rewards you for quick times keeps you focused.  At the same time, there is no timer itself during the game so you can also just play to relax.
